org.alljoyn.bus.annotation
Annotation Type Position

@Documented
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Position

Indicates the numeric position of a field within an AllJoyn struct (Java class). This value defines the order that fields are marshalled and unmarshalled.

Optional Element Summary
 int value
          Position of the field within the AllJoyn struct (Java class).
 

value

public abstract int value
Position of the field within the AllJoyn struct (Java class).

Default:
0
